The paper is about open-domain question answering, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of nearest neighbor search and gated recurrent units, which are common techniques in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with large datasets and scalability, which could fall under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
